{"tid":2287640,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[是靚早] 自煎無精無尿太陽蛋","createTime":"2020-11-16T02:24:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-19T02:59:50.000Z","uid":182895,"like":89,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"3e72b652878958344b857e7e546f9fadc8f26cde","tid":2287640,"uid":182895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T02:24:35.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">[black]多謝大渣哥經理指導我[/black]<br />\n&ldquo;太陽蛋一定係生嘅&rdquo;</span><br />\n(cafe de jargor, 2020)<br />\n<br />\n大渣哥啟發我去唔同嘅黃店追尋優質太陽蛋後再試下自己煎黎做早餐<br />\n<br />\n重温 [大渣哥屌打式大勝] 第一屆太陽蛋大賽<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2282484\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2282484</a><br />\n<br />\n我唔介意有人話我小氣, 我會繼續堅持<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">結果好失望, 煎完隻蛋完全無生蛋白, 沙門氏菌指數偏低, 透明精液又欠奉</span><br />\n睇黎都係要去返大渣哥先食到一定係生嘅太陽蛋<br />\n<br />\n煮<br />\n<br />\n我自己鐘意用泰國蛋<br />\n食得<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m8LLqaY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm8LLqaY.png&h=bfbf9f03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n相比大渣哥果隻真係無地自容<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Tc5juJ4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTc5juJ4.jpg&h=bc8a53a4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4df7ea5ec5cb15bca54f0cc5efb8ac7d2f061858","tid":2287640,"uid":79145,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T02:27:24.000Z","msg":"無沙門氏菌，差評<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw，巴打，煎太陽蛋應該用咩火？個pan洗唔洗燒熱左先？"},{"pid":"18fff87a446633bafaa5587c3d687058094bfeb0","tid":2287640,"uid":182895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4df7ea5ec5cb15bca54f0cc5efb8ac7d2f061858","tid":2287640,"uid":79145,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime